title: Hour 1 - Klay Thompson Ejected, Mike Evans Nothing-burger, Aaron Rodgers Talks Too Much
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Klay Thompson Ejected, Mike Evans Nothing-burger, Aaron Rodgers Talks Too Much
description:
Dan hits on all the latest stories, including Golden State Warriors G Klay Thompson getting ejected for the first time in his career, Tampa Bay Buccaneers WR Mike Evans claim he wasn't giving autographs to referees, and Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers' latest effort to blame his teammates for their struggles.
